# Run this command in Terminal to remove the initial delay while keeping the normal slide‑in animation:

defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-delay -float 0 && defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-time-modifier -float 1.0 && killall Dock

- autohide-delay -float 0 – eliminates the waiting time before the Dock starts to appear.
- autohide-time-modifier -float 1.0 – explicitly sets the animation speed to the default value (normal slide).

# To Revert to the Original Apple Settings:

defaults delete com.apple.dock autohide-delay
defaults delete com.apple.dock autohide-time-modifier
killall Dock
